
This is the server program for the AniTMT animation system.

To install:
1. Unpack this package.
2. If needed, install Perl 5.003 or later
2. If needed, install the following (CPAN) modules:
   - IPC::Shareable (needs Tie::Storeable)  [ both CPAN ]
   - GetOpt::Long                           [ standard ]
   - Time::localtime                        [ standard ]
 
The license can be found in license.eng.txt.

New versions:
  http://www.theofel.de/anitmt/
